User clicks the final "Login" button
User hovers the cursor to "Holidays" and clicks on "Australia Tour Packages"
User selects a specific "Amazing Australia - Winter" package
User selects a travel date
User clicks on "Calculate Price Package"
the system should respond with the "Package Price" page
User reviews the package price and clicks on continue

the system should take the user to the "Traveller Details" page
user enters Traveller1 details: "Rahul" "Kumar" and "123456"
user enters Traveller2 details: "Abhishek" "Kumar" and "654321"
user enters Address for communication: "Rahul" "Kumar" "Patna" "847226"
user checks the box to add this passenger as a payer
user enters PAN details: "Rahul" "12-09-2002" "SEOAK7575B"
user clicks on "Verify"
the system should respond with the message "Invalid Pan Card"
